<plot>At 2 a.m. going on Sunday, September 14th 2003, 28-year old Jonas Markland was found dead in a toilet in a Copenhagen Bar. He had one needle mark in his left arm, and the autopcy indicated that he was killed by an overdose of ketamin. The short film Flush describes that night and the events that led up to the accident.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?198424</url></doc>
